                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker, in Crownstreet. I have a sheet and table-cloth, pawned on the 20th and 26th of August, by a woman; these are the duplicates I gave.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-306-person2221">
                  JOHN 
                  SPENCER
               <interp inst="t18310908-306-person2221" type="surname" value="SPENCER"></interp>
