                     <interp inst="t18310908-306-person2221" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am in the service of a pawnbroker. I have a blanket, pawned on the 19th of August, by a woman. to whom I gave this duplicate.</p>
               <p>MRS. VIDLER. These are all my property; I did not know any thing was missing till I went into the room.</p>
               <p>The prisoner put in a written Defence, stating that they had pawned the goods being in poverty, and that the prosecutrix had agreed to allow them time to redeem them.</p>
               <p>SILAS VIDLER. That was the first pawning; I did not know about these.</p>
